<h3>Design</h3>
<p>The design of the game is similar to the “Breakout” game; however, instead of bouncing balls off of a paddle, you
    have to catch them and then drop them into tanks. Catching the balls takes some practice though, because the
    chamber is circular, and, when the paddle is at the top of the screen, the controls feel backwards.</p>

