<p>After a ball is caught, the paddle turns the color of the ball. The player then has to go to the correct tank and
    drop the ball off before getting the next one. This process is fairly trivial until red balls are introduced. Red
    balls have the ability to knock the ball off of the paddle if touched.</p>

